---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Accessibility"
  description="Accessibility statement for Chiltern Computers - Our commitment to making our services accessible to everyone."
>
  <div class="section-bg-3" style="padding: 120px 20px 80px; min-height: 100vh;">
    <div class="container">
      
      <!-- Page Header -->
      <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 60px;">
        <h1 class="space-font galaxy-text cosmic-glow" style="font-size: clamp(32px, 6vw, 48px); margin-bottom: 16px;">
          Accessibility
        </h1>
        <div style="height: 3px; width: 120px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--solar-orange), var(--mars-red)); margin: 0 auto 20px; border-radius: 2px;"></div>
        <p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--comet-silver); font-size: 16px; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
          Our commitment to providing accessible services and digital experiences for everyone.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Accessibility Content -->
      <div class="cosmic-card" style="padding: 40px; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
        
        <div class="accessibility-section">
          <h2 class="space-font" style="color: var(--solar-orange); font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px;">Our Commitment</h2>
          <p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--starlight-white); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 20px;">
            Chiltern Computers is committed to ensuring digital accessibility for people with disabilities. We are continually improving the user experience for everyone and applying relevant accessibility standards.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="accessibility-section">
          <h2 class="space-font" style="color: var(--solar-orange); font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px;">Website Accessibility</h2>
          <p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--starlight-white); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 12px;">
            Our website is designed to be accessible and user-friendly for all visitors. We strive to meet WCAG 2.1 AA standards through:
          </p>
          <ul class="alien-font" style="color: var(--starlight-white); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 20px; padding-left: 20px;">
            <li>Clear navigation and consistent page structure</li>
            <li>Descriptive link text and image alt tags</li>
            <li>Sufficient color contrast for readability</li>
            <li>Keyboard navigation support</li>
            <li>Responsive design for various screen sizes</li>
            <li>Screen reader compatibility</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="accessibility-section">
          <h2 class="space-font" style="color: var(--solar-orange); font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px;">Physical Accessibility</h2>
          <p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--starlight-white); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 12px;">
            Our Harold Hill location is committed to providing accessible services:
          </p>
          <ul class="alien-font" style="color: var(--starlight-white); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 20px; padding-left: 20px;">
            <li>Ground floor access to our premises</li>
            <li>Home collection and delivery services available</li>
            <li>Flexible appointment scheduling</li>
            <li>Patient and clear communication about technical issues</li>
            <li>Multiple contact methods (phone, email, in-person)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="accessibility-section">
          <h2 class="space-font" style="color: var(--solar-orange); font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px;">Assistive Technology Support</h2>
          <p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--starlight-white); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 20px;">
            We have experience working with various assistive technologies and can provide guidance on computer setups that work well with screen readers, voice recognition software, and other accessibility tools.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="accessibility-section">
          <h2 class="space-font" style="color: var(--solar-orange); font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px;">Communication Preferences</h2>
          <p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--starlight-white); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 12px;">
            We offer multiple ways to communicate and receive support:
          </p>
          <ul class="alien-font" style="color: var(--starlight-white); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 20px; padding-left: 20px;">
            <li>Telephone support with patient explanations</li>
            <li>Email communication for detailed technical discussions</li>
            <li>In-person consultations with visual demonstrations</li>
            <li>Written quotes and service documentation</li>
            <li>Family member or carer involvement welcome</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="accessibility-section">
          <h2 class="space-font" style="color: var(--solar-orange); font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px;">Ongoing Improvements</h2>
          <p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--starlight-white); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 20px;">
            We regularly review our website and services to identify areas for improvement. We welcome feedback from our customers about how we can better serve everyone in our community.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="accessibility-section">
          <h2 class="space-font" style="color: var(--solar-orange); font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px;">Browser and Assistive Technology Compatibility</h2>
          <p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--starlight-white); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 12px;">
            Our website is designed to work with:
          </p>
          <ul class="alien-font" style="color: var(--starlight-white); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 20px; padding-left: 20px;">
            <li>Modern web browsers (Chrome, Firefox, Safari, Edge)</li>
            <li>Screen readers including JAWS, NVDA, and VoiceOver</li>
            <li>Voice recognition software</li>
            <li>Keyboard-only navigation</li>
            <li>Browser zoom up to 200%</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="accessibility-section">
          <h2 class="space-font" style="color: var(--solar-orange); font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px;">Feedback and Support</h2>
          <p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--starlight-white); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 20px;">
            If you encounter any accessibility barriers or have suggestions for improvement, please don't hesitate to contact us. We value your feedback and are committed to addressing any issues promptly.
          </p>
